raw_data.title: Subject Matter Expert – X Level 1

Participates in engineering team activities in a specialized engineering or technology subject area. Contributes to the technical planning process and provides technical guidance.

Utilizes tools, techniques, processes and/or facilities such as state-of-the-art simulation environments, laboratories, and test facilities. Leads engineering team activities in a specialized engineering or technology subject area. Contributes to the technical planning process and provides technical guidance.

raw_data.title: Subject Matter Expert – X Level 3
raw_data.description: Recognized at the industry level in a technical field or specialized engineering or technology area and is proficient in relevant engineering principles and practices. Provides leadership for engineering activities in a specialized engineering or technology subject area. Serves as a major contributor to technical planning process and for providing technical management and guidance.
